f^\prime
 \begin{split} f^\prime (t) &= \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{a^n}{n!}\ e^{(c-bn)t} \\ &= e^{ct}\ \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{1}{n!}\ \left( \frac{a}{e^{bt}}\right)^n\\ &= e^{ct}\ \exp \left( ae^{-bt}\right)\\ &= \exp \left( ct+a\ e^{-bt}\right) \end{split}
f(t)=\sum_{0}^{\infty}\tfrac{a^n}{(n!)(c-bn)}e^{(c-bn)t}
f'(t)=\sum_{0}^{\infty}\tfrac{a^n}{n!}e^{(c-bn)t}=e^{ct}\sum_{0}^{\infty}\tfrac{(a e^{-bt})^n}{n!}=e^{ct+ae^{-bt}}
